profile:
Student Works Painting has been providing top quality painting services at reasonable prices since 1991. Our clients recognize us as the leader in quality and service in the painting industry.

Student Works Painting truly is a student painting company. Meaning all of our Owner / Operators and most of their painters are full-time university students, earning money for tuition and expenses for the following year.

Your satisfaction with both our quality of service and our quality of work is not only important to us but is also part of our business model. Student Works Painting guarantees paint and labour on all projects for a term of three years from date of completion.

Not Sure? No problem. Before we start painting the interior or exterior of your home, StudentWorks Painting sends one of our experts to give you an estimate on your paint job.

profile:
Why Choose Mill Creek Painters?

At Mill Creek Painters, we are proud to say that we are one of the best Residential and Commercial Painting Contractors in Edmonton and in Calgary. With over 25 years experience, we promise our clients to provide the highest quality painting and contracting services at highly competitive rates. We guarantee by the end of the project you will have an environment as unique as you!

To make this possible we offer to all clients:
Outstanding Customer Service: Our staff are available to answer any and all of your questions. Your inquiries will be responded quickly, and regardless of your schedule!

Free In-Home Colour Consultations: House & Condo Painters specially provide free colour consultation before starting the job. We will give you our professional opinion on the colour and finish combinations that will make your home as you dream!

We Only Use High-Quality Paint: We only use well-known and trusted products to deliver the best results for your home. Often working with brands such as Benjamin Moore, Sherwin Williams, Cloverdale, we will never use paint below the "Super" grade. This will ensure you have a high-quality paint job that is washable and durable for years to come. All left-over paint is left with you for future projects.

Experienced Professionals: At Mill Creek Painters we only hire professional, skilled painters for all of our projects. This helps us to ensure that the work we provide is of the highest quality and completed within the shortest amount of time.

profile:
Benny began working for his father as part of a family-owned business that was originally instituted in 1991. Benny has sustained his father’s legacy by incorporating Benny’s Painting Ltd. in 1999. Benny himself has been painting for nearly 25 years and is well-respected for his reliable service and quality workmanship throughout St. Albert and the greater Edmonton area.


Benny’s Painting does it all! Ranging from a residential minor drywall patch & paint touch-up to a major commercial painting project, our experienced crew of full-time employees can handle it! Throughout the entire project, from methodical preparation through to careful cleanup, you can expect the job will be done right.


We take care in our job. Our team is trained in safe practices and follow the safety guidelines set out for them. Nonetheless, Benny ensures his full-time employees are covered by the Workers Compensation Board. Benny’s Painting Ltd. also carries a comprehensive liability insurance policy for contingency. As our valued customer, you can relax and rest-assured that the job will get done with care.
